OL,3,CThe Olympic torch visits the Channel
OL,4,CIslands
OL,6,FThe Olympic Torch has made a surprise
OL,7,Fvisit to Guernsey.
OL,9,FThe Olympic Committee invited a group
OL,10,Fof lucky islanders to see the Paris
OL,11,F2024 torch at Hauteville House - where
OL,12,FVictor Hugo, writer of Les Miserable,
OL,13,Flived during his exile from France in
OL,14,Fthe 19th Century.
