OL,3,CThe Olympic torch visits the Channel
OL,4,CIslands
OL,6,FGuernsey was not on the official route
OL,7,Fof the Olympic Torch, but organisers
OL,8,Fand torchbearers attended a private
OL,9,Fceremony on Monday 1 July. Hauteville
OL,10,FHouse is owned by the city of Paris
OL,11,Fand holds significant historical and
OL,12,Fcultural importance to the French.
OL,14,FThe torchbearers included Specsavers
OL,15,Fco-founder Dame Mary Perkins, a French
OL,16,Fpoet, and the great-great-grandson of
OL,17,FVictor Hugo, Jean-Baptiste Hugo.
