OL,3,CThe Olympic torch visits the Channel
OL,4,CIslands
OL,6,FThe first Olympic Torch of the relay
OL,7,Fwas lit at the main site of the
OL,8,Fancient Olympics in Greece on Tuesday
OL,9,F16 April.
OL,11,FThe official relay then began three
OL,12,Fweeks later, touring around France and
OL,13,Fother French colonies.
OL,15,FThe Paris 2024 torch's design draws
OL,16,Finspiration from the themes of the
OL,17,Fyear's Games: Equality, Water, and
OL,18,FPeacefulness.
