OL,3,CThe Olympic torch visits the Channel
OL,4,CIslands
OL,6,FDame Mary Perkins was chosen as a
OL,7,Ftorchbearer for Guernsey - she said
OL,8,Fshe was "lost for words".
OL,10,FShe added: "Guernsey is so good at
OL,11,Fsport and I think it starts very young
OL,12,F- you've heard the saying before that
OL,13,Fwe punch above our weight.
OL,15,F"So how applicable and how good is it
OL,16,Fthat the Olympic torch came here."
